TITLE: Complete FastAPI Application Example
DESCRIPTION: Full example of a FastAPI application implementing Permit.io permission checks
SOURCE: https://github.com/permitio/docs/blob/master/versioned_docs/version-1.0.0/tutorials/_quickstart-parts/_quickstart_python.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_10

