LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
@PostMapping("/login")
public ResponseEntity<?> login(@RequestBody LoginRequest request) {
    Ticket ticket = permit.elements().loginAs(request.getUserId(), request.getTenant());
    ResponseCookie cookie = ResponseCookie.from("permit_token", ticket.getToken())
            .httpOnly(true)
            .secure(true)
            .sameSite("Strict")
            .build();
    return ResponseEntity.ok()
            .header(HttpHeaders.SET_COOKIE, cookie.toString())
            .body(Map.of("redirect_url", ticket.getRedirectUrl()));
}
```

