SOURCE: https://github.com/permitio/docs/blob/master/docs/modeling/mesa-verde.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
resource "permitio_role" "Sender" {
  key         = "Sender"
  name        = "Sender"
  resource    = permitio_resource.Transaction.key
  permissions = ["list"]
  depends_on  = [permitio_resource.Transaction]
}
```

